dal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 27, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mtt1665702962540.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mtt1665702962540.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mtt1665702962540.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mtt1665702962540\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">Environment Considerations for SQLite\n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mtt1665702962540__environment_considerations_for_sqlite_171477\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">It is strongly recommended that you have the SQLite database on a local drive.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mtt1665702962540__p_d58370e1_d58371e1_d58372e1\">SQLite has limited support for concurrent access. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lct1665702664877.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lct1665702664877.html\" title=\"The SQLite database has very limited support for concurrency. This has implications for the default locking strategy, hit list behavior, and transaction length.\">Locking Considerations for SQLite</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mtt1665702962540__p_d58373e1_d58374e1_d58375e1\">The SQLite documentation recommends:</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"mtt1665702962540__note_w18ab1b5b7_w19ab1b5_w20ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If you have many client programs accessing a common database over a network,\n      you should consider using a client/server database engine instead of SQLite. Consult the\n      SQLite documentation for more information. (<a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://www.sqlite.org/whentouse.html\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sqlite.org/whentouse.html</a>)</div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530071\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530071\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Environment Considerations for SQLite Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 27, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Environment Considerations for SQLite It is strongly recommended that you have the SQLite database on a local drive. SQLite has limited support for concurrent access. For more information, see Locking Considerations for SQLite . The SQLite documentation recommends: Note: If you have many client programs accessing a common database over a network, you should consider using a client/server database engine instead of SQLite. Consult the SQLite documentation for more information. ( https://www.sqlite.org/whentouse.html ) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}